Healthy Highlights

Sign Up For Our E-Newsletter

Featuring a monthly dose of information and inspiration for living well.

Eligibility Services

The team may be able to help you get health coverage from federal, state or county programs.

We Are ER

Quality care - when minutes count. The ER teams' focus is on the patient experience, a higher level of care and striving to achieve the shortest ER wait times.

Urgent Care - Get In Line, Online

RediMed and Medstat urgent cares offer online check in for in-office and telehealth (video) visits to treat life's little illnesses and injuries.

Schedule Your Appointment Today

Telehealth (video) and in-person visits are open for new and existing Lutheran Health Physicians patients. Call 833-LHN-4YOU (833-546-4968) or schedule an appointment online.

Contact Us

Have questions about the facility, job opportunities or your stay? Connect with us today.
